.TH avp 1  "avp 0.5.0" 
.SH NAME
avp \- Agent Validator Protocol \- Claude Code hook processor
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBavp\fR [\fB\-d\fR|\fB\-\-debug\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
AVP \- Agent Validator Protocol
.PP
Claude Code hook processor that validates tool calls, file changes, and more.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-d\fR, \fB\-\-debug\fR
Enable debug output to stderr
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
avp\-init(1)
Install AVP hooks into Claude Code settings
.TP
avp\-deinit(1)
Remove AVP hooks from Claude Code settings and delete .avp directory
.TP
avp\-doctor(1)
Diagnose AVP configuration and setup
.TP
avp\-list(1)
List all available validators
.TP
avp\-login(1)
Authenticate with the AVP registry
.TP
avp\-logout(1)
Log out from the AVP registry
.TP
avp\-whoami(1)
Show current authenticated user
.TP
avp\-search(1)
Search the AVP registry for packages
.TP
avp\-info(1)
Show detailed information about a package
.TP
avp\-install(1)
Install a package from the registry
.TP
avp\-uninstall(1)
Remove an installed package
.TP
avp\-new(1)
Create a new RuleSet from template
.TP
avp\-publish(1)
Publish a package to the registry
.TP
avp\-unpublish(1)
Remove a published package version from the registry
.TP
avp\-outdated(1)
Check for available package updates
.TP
avp\-update(1)
Update installed packages to latest versions
.TP
avp\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH VERSION
v0.5.0
